snippet.title: Kyub Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Kyub has been released on Xbox One, July 13th 2016.
Kyub will be released on the Windows store, January 17th 2017

Available on Xbox One store: https://www.microsoft.com/store/p/kyub/brmrvl00xv67

Puzzle games are seeing a revival on consoles and Kyub is taking the lead! Move the “Kyub” and use its abilities to solve devious puzzles and escape malicious traps. With more than 80 stages the mysterious world of Kyub offers simple mechanics yet a deep gameplay with thousands of combinations!
